{"tid":1853982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護全部讀書人，醫生全部尖子，柒婆講埋d垃圾邊個會信","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T17:09:34.000Z","uid":208376,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e81f9d3e9b14532d13e076409343acd56fd73b","tid":1853982,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:20:29.000Z","msg":"當佢地係popo廢老?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟做俾邊個睇?"},{"pid":"08d52dc4f854c4a6a465896c4f6469b0f1929426","tid":1853982,"uid":64337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"佢考第一 好威㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a2f6971050318121563c7ee1a65c63beea6745","tid":1853982,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6DwikwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=7a8dc6e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c625068ebb8ae1cb35ac82d61ad12632d5bc2189","tid":1853982,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"無睇到<br />\n佢講左乜9<br />\n我無乜讀書睇佢呃唔呃到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732adf2fc2e3aadc16330ba2cee2fcfcf1af2091","tid":1853982,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"廢老信"},{"pid":"6754535808389a4f87393110a1b6428c3d04b2e8","tid":1853982,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"林鄭年年第一架<br />\n<br />\n班醫生咪當年讀書啲手下敗將囉"},{"pid":"ce09acb479f5df34a899ca48cc7bde81dfbdff52","tid":1853982,"uid":102993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"未必架，唔少私人診所醫生都成日喺非應診期間用 Whatsapp ，向病人時常發表個人政見，例如: 黃基林醫生，會使用仇恨性言語罵人曱甴。<br />\n<br />\n資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edr.hk/doctor/info/wong-kee-lam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edr.hk%2Fdoctor%2Finfo%2Fwong-kee-lam&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6DwikwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=fa66e2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edr.hk/doctor/info/wong-kee-lam</a>"},{"pid":"bd282ed34eb49b89a949f59155b04188e53aaf48","tid":1853982,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08d52dc4f854c4a6a465896c4f6469b0f192